---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const proposalHref = `${base.replace(/\/$/, '')}/GenJ_Proposal.pdf`;
---
<section id="contact" style="padding-bottom: 32px">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-panel">
      <div>
        <span class="badge">CONTACT</span>
        <h3>함께 만들 파트너를 찾습니다.</h3>
        <p>교육기관 · 대학 · 공공기관 · 기술 파트너 — GenJ 교육법과 플랫폼을 함께 검증·고도화할 분들과 만나고 싶습니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn btn-light" href="mailto:soonsoon@soonsoons.com">
          협업 문의
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M3 7h8m0 0L7 3m4 4l-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href={proposalHref} download="GenJ_Proposal.pdf">제안서 다운로드</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-panel {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--grad-brand);
    border-radius: 28px;
    padding: 48px;
    color: #fff;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    gap: 32px; align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(124,58,237,0.3);
  }
  .cta-panel::before, .cta-panel::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(60px);
    opacity: 0.4;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cta-panel::before { width: 400px; height: 400px; background: var(--cyan-300); top: -200px; right: -100px; }
  .cta-panel::after  { width: 300px; height: 300px; background: var(--amber-300); bottom: -150px; left: -50px; opacity: 0.25; }

  .badge {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  }
  h3 {
    position: relative;
    font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
    line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  p { position: relative; opacity: 0.92; max-width: 50ch; line-height: 1.6; }

  .actions { position: relative; display: flex; gap: 10px; flex-shrink: 0; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .actions a {
    padding: 13px 22px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-weight: 500; font-size: 15px;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s, background .2s;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .btn-light {
    background: #fff; color: var(--violet-700);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
  }
  .btn-light:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.25); }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    color: #fff;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.22); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .cta-panel { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 32px; }
  }
</style>
